    OMRSTopicListener, OMRSTopicRepositoryEventListener
    public class DevOpsOMRSTopicListener
extends OMRSTopicListenerBase
    DevOpsOMRSTopicListener received details of each OMRS event from the cohorts that the local server is connected to. It passes NEW_ENTITY_EVENTs to the publisher.
